Text: Hi Boyestas I write you because I mess you and all your family I hope every body are ok Maricela say hi How are Ange Martin and Alma Ryne my uncle say hi to every one Well I back to the work PS maybe I call to the Saturday or Sunday Antonio Paez Purchasing and Imports Assistant

RE Hiboy How are you I thing Mexico are better than USA Let me call you Original Message From mailto Sent Wednesday February PM To Antonio Paez Subject Re Hi Forwarded by John GriffithCorpEnron on AM John Griffith AM To Antonio Paez cc Subject Re Hi Document link John Griffith Tony Whats up Hey I think that Mexico is playing US tomorrow in Ohio for the World Cup qualifying Is Mexico any good Should we wager on the match Hope things are going well with you Talk to you soon My work number is if you want to call me anytime I got a promotion I am now trading Natural Gas Options We trade them over the internet also We have a website Enron Online that we make markets on many different commodities and we just started making option markets in natural gas a couple of months ago I am helping with this Tell your family hi and have a great day John
